# Quick Reference - What Changed Where

## File-by-File Changes

### 1️⃣ `web/control/control.js` (Main Logic File)

#### Added: Fuzzy Matching Utilities (Lines 506-573)
```javascript
// NEW: Normalize tags for matching
normalizeTag(tag)
  └─ Converts: "Basketball" → "basketball"

// NEW: Calculate similarity between strings
levenshteinDistance(a, b)
  └─ Returns: edit distance between strings

// NEW: Get confidence score (0-1) for match
calculateTagSimilarity(input, candidate)
  └─ Returns: similarity score

// NEW: Find best event match from catalog
fuzzyMatchEventTag(input, eventCatalog)
  └─ Returns: { match, confidence, matches[] }
```

#### Modified: Context Logic (Line 1733)
```javascript
// OLD:
function activeContextOrWarn() {
  if (activeContext) return activeContext;
  showToast("Start an event context before scoring.", "warn");
  return null;  // BLOCKS SCORING
}

// NEW:
function activeContextOrWarn() {
  if (activeContext) return activeContext;
  return {
    // Auto-creates default context (NO LONGER BLOCKS)
    category: "", event: "", subevent: "",
    reason: "Untagged", notes: "",
    isDefault: true
  };
}
```

#### Modified: Audit Entry Builder (Lines 1760-1776)
```javascript
// OLD: function buildAppliedAuditEntry({
//   type, summary, changes, context, reason, notes,
//   beforeScores, afterScores, extra
// })

// NEW: function buildAppliedAuditEntry({
//   type, summary, changes, context, reason, notes,
//   eventTag: "",  // ← NEW PARAMETER
//   beforeScores, afterScores, extra
// })

// And stores: { ..., eventTag, eventTagNormalized: normalizeTag(eventTag), ... }
```

#### Added: Tag UI Functions (Lines 966-1044)
```javascript
renderTagSuggestions(input)
  └─ Shows fuzzy-matched event suggestions

addTagChip(tag)
  └─ Creates blue chip element for selected tag

getSelectedTags()
  └─ Returns array of currently selected tags
```

#### Modified: Scoring Action (Lines 2015-2045)
```javascript
// OLD: submitScoringAction({ type, summary, changes })
//   └─ No event tag handling

// NEW: submitScoringAction({ type, summary, changes })
//   const selectedTags = getSelectedTags()
//   const eventTag = selectedTags[0] || ""
//   └─ Extracts and passes eventTag with score
```

#### Modified: Proposal Submission (Line 1952)
```javascript
// OLD: async function submitProposal({
//   actionType, summary, changes, context, reason, notes, pathRequest
// })

// NEW: async function submitProposal({
//   actionType, summary, changes, context, reason, notes,
//   eventTag: "",  // ← NEW PARAMETER
//   pathRequest
// })
```

#### Added: Event Listeners (Lines 3217-3243)
```javascript
// Wire up tag selector UI:
tagSelectorToggle.addEventListener("change", ...)
  └─ Shows/hides tag selector panel

tagSearchInput.addEventListener("input", ...)
  └─ Debounced 150ms, calls renderTagSuggestions()
```

