### 2️⃣ `web/control/index.html` (UI Markup)

#### Removed (Old Complex Structure)
```html
<!-- DELETED: Complex nested event selectors -->
<div class="reason-lock-controls-grid">
  <select id="categorySelect"></select>
  <select id="eventSelect"></select>
  <select id="subeventSelect"></select>
  <select id="eventModeSelect"></select>
  <input id="seasonInput">
  <input id="sessionInput">
</div>

<!-- DELETED: Confusing reason builder rows -->
<select id="reasonTemplateSelect"></select>
<input id="reasonDetailInput">
<button id="useReasonTemplateBtn"></button>

<select id="usedReasonSelect"></select>
<button id="applyUsedReasonBtn"></button>
```

#### Replace With (New 3-Step Form)
```html
<!-- NEW: Simple 3-step form structure -->
<div class="quick-scoring-form">

  <!-- STEP 1: Reason -->
  <div class="form-step">
    <label class="form-label">Step 1: Select Reason</label>
    <select id="reasonTemplateSelect"></select>
    <input id="customReasonInput" placeholder="Or type custom reason...">
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 2: Details -->
  <div class="form-step">
    <label class="form-label">Step 2: Optional Details</label>
    <input id="notesInput" placeholder="Notes (who, what, detail)">
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 3: Tag (Collapsible) -->
  <div class="form-step form-step-expand">
    <label class="expand-toggle">
      <input type="checkbox" id="tagSelectorToggle" />
      <span>Step 3: Tag Event (Optional)</span>
      <span class="expand-icon">▶</span>
    </label>

    <div class="tag-selector-section" hidden id="tagSelectorPanel">
      <input id="tagSearchInput" placeholder="Search or add tag...">
      <div id="tagSuggestions"></div>
      <div id="selectedTags" class="tag-chips"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
```

---

### 3️⃣ `web/control/control.css` (Styling)

#### Added (Lines 1614-1705)
```css
/* Form Layout */
.quick-scoring-form { display: grid; gap: 14px; }
.form-step { display: grid; gap: 8px; }
.form-label { font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); }

/* Expand Toggle */
.expand-toggle { display: flex; gap: 8px; cursor: pointer; }
.expand-icon { transition: transform 200ms ease; }
.expand-toggle input:checked ~ .expand-icon { transform: rotate(90deg); }

/* Tag Suggestions */
.tag-suggestions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
.tag-suggestion-item {
  padding: 4px 10px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  background: var(--surface-tint);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 150ms ease;
}
.tag-suggestion-item:hover { background: var(--accent); color: white; }

/* Tag Chips */
.tag-chip {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  padding: 6px 12px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: var(--accent);
  color: white;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.tag-chip-remove { cursor: pointer; background: none; border: 0; color: white; }

/* Animations */
@keyframes slideDown {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-8px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
```

