## Summary by Impact

### 🔴 Removed (Breaking Changes)
- ❌ Blocking "Start Context" requirement
- ❌ Forced event category/event/subevent selection
- ❌ Session name requirement for one-time events

### 🟢 Added (New Features)
- ✅ Fuzzy event matching (catches typos)
- ✅ Collapsible tag selector
- ✅ Event tag data fields in Firestore
- ✅ Tag chips UI
- ✅ Automatic context creation

### 🟡 Modified (Behavior Changes)
- 🔄 Scoring now works immediately (before: blocked)
- 🔄 Events now optional tags (before: required structure)
- 🔄 Reason simplified (before: complex builder)

### 🔵 Preserved (Unchanged)
- ✓ House scoring system
- ✓ Quick buttons (±50, ±30, etc)
- ✓ History tracking
- ✓ Approval queue
- ✓ Backup/restore
- ✓ All permissions system
- ✓ Data format (backward compatible)

